<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Monthly Borrow Report</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Monthly Borrow Records Report</h2>
    <p>Dear Admin,</p>

    <p>
      The borrow records report for <span class="highlight"><%= month %></span> is ready.
      You can find the detailed data in the attached Excel file.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please review the report and take any necessary actions.
    </p>

    <p class="footer">
      â€” Library Management System<br>
      Please do not reply to this automated message.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
